comments: Yes. It is hard to get such a course at undergraduate level about such an important person in Western philosophy. Should immediately take it if it is offered again (once in every few years). Class size is terrific. Only 6 people ended up taking the class.
Yes, you should take this class! I feel as if I have had a thorough introduction to Plato. Even better, I now have a desire to read and understand his works better as I continue in life.
